data.description: At almost 1500 sqft, this 2 bed, 2 bath top level corner condo in The Reserve Condominiums overlooks a winding creek and backs to trees, providing a serene atmosphere to enjoy your morning cup of coffee. This well-maintained home includes a formal dining room, light-filled living room with balcony access and an eat-in kitchen with stainless steel appliances including a new range. The primary bedroom and ensuite bath features a separate shower, soaking tub, double vanity and two large walk-in closets. An in unit laundry, secondary bedroom, second bathroom, and one-car garage with extra storage space complete the home. Community amenities include a pool and a clubhouse. Conveniently located near Hemlock Overlook Regional Park and Signal Hill Park  as well as shopping, restaurant and the VRE make this the ideal place to call home. Welcome home to Holmes Place!  OPEN HOUSE -  SATURDAY 4/6 & SUNDAY 4/7, 2-4PM
